gource
------------------------------------------
OpenGL-based 3D visualisation tool for source control repositories.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.5-1
  libGLEW2.1-2.1.0-1
  libGLU1-9.0.2-1
  libSDL2_2.0_0-2.0.7-1
  libSDL2_image2.0_0-2.0.2-1
  libboost_filesystem1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_system1.66-1.66.0-1
  libfreetype6-2.12.1-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libpcre2_8_0-10.42-1
  libpng16-1.6.37-1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  libtinyxml0-2.6.2-1bl3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.40-1
  cygport-0.36.0-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libGLEW-devel-2.1.0-1
  libGLU-devel-9.0.2-1
  libSDL2-devel-2.0.7-1
  libSDL2_image-devel-2.0.2-1
  libboost-devel-1.66.0-1
  libfreetype-devel-2.12.1-1
  libpcre2-devel-10.42-1
  libpng-devel-1.6.37-1
  libtinyxml-devel-2.6.2-1bl3
  make-4.4-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/acaudwell/Gource

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/acaudwell/Gource/releases/download/gource-0.54/gource-0.54.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gource-0.54-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gource-0.54-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gource-0.54-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gource-0.54-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gource)
  /usr/bin/gource.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gource.README
  /usr/share/doc/gource/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/gource/ChangeLog
